# Canonical Commands Gate

Use ONLY commands defined in @docs/project-config.md.

Minimum set per PR:
- Install (`npm install`)
- Lint (`npm run lint`)
- Typecheck (if applicable) (`npm run typecheck`)
- Test (`npm run test`)
- Build (`npm run build`)

Additional commands referenced in `@docs/project-config.md`:
- Dev (`npm run dev`)
- E2E (optional) (`npm run test:e2e`)

If API exists:
- OpenAPI validate command (`npm run openapi:validate`)

If schemas exist:
- JSON Schema validate command (`npm run schema:validate`)

If Supabase used:
- Ensure access control tests exist for owner-only / role-based behavior.
